data.value:
Hello, this is the instruction how to use this application.
1) To add a flight to the database, click "Main Func -> Add"
2) To update or delete a flight in the database, check if the proper mode enabled and double click on a row you want to Update/Delete
3) To switch between "Update" and "Delete" mods choose whatever you need in "Main Func" menu
4) To find a flight in the database, click "Main Func -> Find" and enter some information in opened window.
5) To show all flights click "Main Func -> Reset"
